videos.description: Samajae Haynes-Jones dives to the basket and switches hands in the air on the lay-in.
videos.headline: Haynes-Jones gets sweet layup for Wichita St.

videos.description: Conner Frankamp moves the ball around and eventually finds Zach Brown who drains a 3-ball for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Frankamp sets up Brown 3-pointer

videos.description: Connor Frankamp finishes the first half strong with a long-range jumper vs. Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Frankamp ends first half with 12 points

videos.description: Connor Frankamp makes the drive and finds Rashard Kelly under the basket who puts it through.
videos.headline: Frankamp finds Kelly for a dunk

videos.description: Notre Dame comes down with the rebound and Matt Farrell drains a 3-pointer to cut Wichita St's lead.
videos.headline: Notre Dame answers with a Farrell 3-ball

videos.description: Matt Farrell drives to the basket and gets a foul on the lay-in to make it a three point play for the Irish.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Farrell draws foul on layup

videos.description: Landry Shamet find Shaquille Morris under the basket and he throws down a big slam for Wichita St.
videos.headline: Shamet finds Morris for huge dunk

videos.description: Landry Shamet hits a mid-range jumper to extend the Shockers lead to three late in the second half.
videos.headline: Shamet makes timely jumper

videos.description: Matt Farrell forces a turnover that leads to a Notre Dame bucket making it a one point game with just 13 seconds left.
videos.headline: Farrell steal leads to Colson jumper

videos.description: Martinas Geben makes both of his free throws to put the Fighting Irish in the lead and on the last play of the game, Landy Shamet turns the ball over sealing Notre Dame's victory.
videos.headline: Geben FTs and Shamet turnover lead to Notre Dame win

videos.description: Notre Dame head coach Mike Brey says the leadership on his was the key to their 67-66 upset over Wichita State.
videos.headline: Brey thrilled for his players to win Maui Invitational
